<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="question-n">question <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'kwestʃən/    美 /'kwestʃən/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-answer">1.★ <strong>问题 【反 answer】；难题：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There is no single answer to the question.
这个问题的答案不是唯一的。</p><footer>外研⑧ – 6</footer></div>

<h3 id="problem-question">辨析 problem, question</h3>
<p>二者都可译作“问题”。<br />
<strong>problem</strong>  指客观存在等待解决的“问题”，强调困难。
<strong>question</strong> 指对某事怀疑而提出等待回答的“问题”，着重疑惑和不能断定。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’d like to put a question to the speaker. 
我想向发言人提一个问题。</p></div>

<h4 id="2u">2.<strong>[U] 怀疑：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is by far the best. There is <strong>no question about it</strong> (= it is completely certain).
他显然是最好的。这毫无疑问。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="out-of-question">out of question</h3>
<p>1.<strong>毫无疑问</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="out-of-the-question">out of the question</h3>
<p>1.<strong>不可能的</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="in-question">in question</h3>
<p>1.<strong>讨论中的；有疑问的；不确定的</strong>  </p></div>